{"tid":147021,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"勞工法例一問 HR巴絲入","createTime":"2017-03-07T14:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T04:44:01.000Z","uid":64261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0078365e1987f75890524d4d6c0c9a9fba7c9039","tid":147021,"uid":64261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:25:49.000Z","msg":"想問下各巴絲HR勞工問題<br />\n1）有醫生證明病假如何計算 ？ <br />\n（包括試用期間/過了試用期）<br />\n例如：月薪9000 一日病假 <br />\n例如：月薪9000 連續五日有醫生證明病假<br />\n<br />\n會照出糧/出四分五日薪 ？<br />\n係月薪除當月總日子 /直接統一除30日 /工作天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上勞工網睇到頭都大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e42279ab4d32f76efa5d771d509d41bd54992c","tid":147021,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"應該扣 月薪除工作日？？<br />\n同埋果五日出4/5糧"},{"pid":"8ad08030e7f03def5b51e038fc11880924a8bde4","tid":147021,"uid":64261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該扣 月薪除工作日？？<br />\n同埋果五日出4/5糧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇就4/5糧 <br />\n但果日日薪點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937f70be7f1704ebe97c6dc44e545b53907c28f4","tid":147021,"uid":33806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下各巴絲HR勞工問題<br />\n1）有醫生證明病假如何計算 ？ <br />\n（包括試用期間/過了試用期）<br />\n例如：月薪9000 一日病假 <br />\n例如：月薪9000 連續五日有醫生證明病假<br />\n<br />\n會照出糧/出四分五日薪 ？<br />\n係月薪除當月總日子 /直接統一除30日 /工作天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上勞工網睇到頭都大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟正例呢<br />\n一日病假，除非係工傷，唔係就冇錢<br />\n連續五日有醫生紙又夠病假額，就出五份四<br />\n邊個數既五份四呢？<br />\n精彩喇，要計返放病假前對上十二個月平均日薪<br />\n再乘五份四<br />\n<br />\n簡單d講絶少HR會跟足法定計法<br />\n因為複雜到近乎戇鳩"},{"pid":"7c83f3fc71e4db19d8d454d63babb6c4d82b2eec","tid":147021,"uid":28396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下各巴絲HR勞工問題<br />\n1）有醫生證明病假如何計算 ？ <br />\n（包括試用期間/過了試用期）<br />\n例如：月薪9000 一日病假 <br />\n例如：月薪9000 連續五日有醫生證明病假<br />\n<br />\n會照出糧/出四分五日薪 ？<br />\n係月薪除當月總日子 /直接統一除30日 /工作天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上勞工網睇到頭都大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟正例呢<br />\n一日病假，除非係工傷，唔係就冇錢<br />\n連續五日有醫生紙又夠病假額，就出五份四<br />\n邊個數既五份四呢？<br />\n精彩喇，要計返放病假前對上十二個月平均日薪<br />\n再乘五份四<br />\n<br />\n簡單d講絶少HR會跟足法定計法<br />\n因為複雜到近乎戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔可以話on9，有啲工種出糧唔係定額，有需要拉平均計"},{"pid":"74b16fd0cecbcfd81a0242b53639f2941c608961","tid":147021,"uid":64261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下各巴絲HR勞工問題<br />\n1）有醫生證明病假如何計算 ？ <br />\n（包括試用期間/過了試用期）<br />\n例如：月薪9000 一日病假 <br />\n例如：月薪9000 連續五日有醫生證明病假<br />\n<br />\n會照出糧/出四分五日薪 ？<br />\n係月薪除當月總日子 /直接統一除30日 /工作天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上勞工網睇到頭都大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟正例呢<br />\n一日病假，除非係工傷，唔係就冇錢<br />\n連續五日有醫生紙又夠病假額，就出五份四<br />\n邊個數既五份四呢？<br />\n精彩喇，要計返放病假前對上十二個月平均日薪<br />\n再乘五份四<br />\n<br />\n簡單d講絶少HR會跟足法定計法<br />\n因為複雜到近乎戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔可以話on9，有啲工種出糧唔係定額，有需要拉平均計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但一日病假就冇補水 ？ <br />\n同埋想問有啲寫明一個月得兩日病假 <br />\n但如果要請兩日以上又點計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1c6091dd0528a61fee11f1a55739fe863f12b2","tid":147021,"uid":33806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下各巴絲HR勞工問題<br />\n1）有醫生證明病假如何計算 ？ <br />\n（包括試用期間/過了試用期）<br />\n例如：月薪9000 一日病假 <br />\n例如：月薪9000 連續五日有醫生證明病假<br />\n<br />\n會照出糧/出四分五日薪 ？<br />\n係月薪除當月總日子 /直接統一除30日 /工作天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上勞工網睇到頭都大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟正例呢<br />\n一日病假，除非係工傷，唔係就冇錢<br />\n連續五日有醫生紙又夠病假額，就出五份四<br />\n邊個數既五份四呢？<br />\n精彩喇，要計返放病假前對上十二個月平均日薪<br />\n再乘五份四<br />\n<br />\n簡單d講絶少HR會跟足法定計法<br />\n因為複雜到近乎戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔可以話on9，有啲工種出糧唔係定額，有需要拉平均計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但一日病假就冇補水 ？ <br />\n同埋想問有啲寫明一個月得兩日病假 <br />\n但如果要請兩日以上又點計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n法例係要連續四日先有錢<br />\